        {
          "html": "<div style=\"--color-royal-plum:#23002b;--color-hot-pink:#e894ff;--color-neon-green:#93ffe4;--color-sunburst-orange:#ffac47;--color-forest-shard:#002629;--color-espresso-chip:#291900;--color-pure-white:#ffffff;--color-deep-plum:#db99f7;--font-druk:Anton,sans-serif;--font-neue:Inter,sans-serif;background:var(--color-royal-plum);padding:48px 32px;box-sizing:border-box;width:100%;font-family:var(--font-neue);\"><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue);font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.08em;color:var(--color-hot-pink);margin:0 0 12px 0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Why Join</p><h2 style=\"font-family:var(--font-druk);font-size:52px;line-height:0.85;letter-spacing:0.005em;color:var(--color-pure-white);margin:0 0 32px 0;text-transform:uppercase;\">What You Get</h2><div style=\"display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"background:var(--color-forest-shard);border-radius:14px;padding:28px 28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--color-neon-green);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><circle cx=\"10\" cy=\"7\" r=\"3\" stroke=\"#93ffe4\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M4 17c0-3.3 2.7-6 6-6s6 2.7 6 6\" stroke=\"#93ffe4\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-druk);font-size:32px;line-height:0.85;color:var(--color-neon-green);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Network Access</h3><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.43;letter-spacing:-0.022em;color:var(--color-pure-white);opacity:0.75;margin:0;\">Connect directly with 500+ founders, investors, and changemakers who are building the future — no boring mixers, just real relationships.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-espresso-chip);border-radius:14px;padding:28px 28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--color-sunburst-orange);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><rect x=\"3\" y=\"5\" width=\"14\" height=\"10\" rx=\"2\" stroke=\"#ffac47\" stroke-width=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M7 9h6M7 12h4\" stroke=\"#ffac47\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-druk);font-size:32px;line-height:0.85;color:var(--color-sunburst-orange);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Exclusive Events</h3><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.43;letter-spacing:-0.022em;color:var(--color-pure-white);opacity:0.75;margin:0;\">Curated dinners, rooftop sessions, and invite-only experiences in cities worldwide. Events designed to spark meaningful dialogue and bold ideas.</p></div><div style=\"background:var(--color-hot-pink);border-radius:14px;padding:28px 28px 32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px;\"><div style=\"width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:50%;border:1.5px solid var(--color-royal-plum);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M10 3l1.8 5.4H17l-4.6 3.4 1.8 5.4L10 14l-4.2 3.2 1.8-5.4L3 8.4h5.2z\" stroke=\"#23002b\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/></svg></div><h3 style=\"font-family:var(--font-druk);font-size:32px;line-height:0.85;color:var(--color-royal-plum);margin:0;text-transform:uppercase;\">Champion Impact</h3><p style=\"font-family:var(--font-neue);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.43;letter-spacing:-0.022em;color:var(--color-royal-plum);opacity:0.8;margin:0;\">Amplify your work and be part of a collective committed to positive change — backed by a community that believes in doing good while doing well.</p></div></div></div>",
